[
  {
    "start": 0.1,
    "end": 4.902,
    "text": "If an AI Agent reads a malicious page, should it still act for you?",
    "segmentId": "c01-p01-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p01",
    "id": "cue-001"
  },
  {
    "start": 5.278,
    "end": 10.162,
    "text": "OpenAI warns that prompt injection now looks less like an obvious command",
    "segmentId": "c01-p02-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p02",
    "id": "cue-002"
  },
  {
    "start": 10.162,
    "end": 14.716,
    "text": "and more like social engineering designed to mislead an agent in context.",
    "segmentId": "c01-p02-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p02",
    "id": "cue-003"
  },
  {
    "start": 14.716,
    "end": 18.965,
    "text": "Picture a dinner-planning agent that almost sends your home address to a",
    "segmentId": "c01-p03-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p03",
    "id": "cue-004"
  },
  {
    "start": 18.965,
    "end": 22.785,
    "text": "fake verification site while trying to reserve a table for your family.",
    "segmentId": "c01-p03-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p03",
    "id": "cue-005"
  },
  {
    "start": 22.785,
    "end": 27.572,
    "text": "By the end, you will have a three-tier AI agent action permission matrix:",
    "segmentId": "c01-p04-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p04",
    "id": "cue-006"
  },
  {
    "start": 27.572,
    "end": 32.491,
    "text": "what can run automatically, what needs informed confirmation, and what must",
    "segmentId": "c01-p04-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p04",
    "id": "cue-007"
  },
  {
    "start": 32.491,
    "end": 32.864,
    "text": "be blocked.",
    "segmentId": "c01-p04-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p04",
    "id": "cue-008"
  },
  {
    "start": 32.864,
    "end": 37.069,
    "text": "The key question is not only, “Can the agent spot the bad sentence?",
    "segmentId": "c01-p05-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p05",
    "id": "cue-009"
  },
  {
    "start": 37.069,
    "end": 41.546,
    "text": "It is, “What could this sentence make the agent do if the agent is fooled?",
    "segmentId": "c01-p05-u02",
    "sceneId": "c01-p05",
    "id": "cue-010"
  },
  {
    "start": 41.546,
    "end": 46.487,
    "text": "This video is packed with practical, high-value insights to help you get",
    "segmentId": "c01-p06-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p06",
    "id": "cue-011"
  },
  {
    "start": 46.487,
    "end": 47.23,
    "text": "better at using AI.",
    "segmentId": "c01-p06-u01",
    "sceneId": "c01-p06",
    "id": "cue-012"
  },
  {
    "start": 47.23,
    "end": 52.481,
    "text": "It's a longer one, so follow Tiny Agent and save it so you don't lose it.",
    "segmentId": "c01-p06-u02",
    "sceneId": "c01-p06",
    "id": "cue-013"
  },
  {
    "start": 52.481,
    "end": 54.448,
    "text": "Start with a familiar task.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p01-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p01",
    "id": "cue-014"
  },
  {
    "start": 54.448,
    "end": 59.332,
    "text": "You ask an AI agent to find a restaurant for a family birthday, compare",
    "segmentId": "c02-p01-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p01",
    "id": "cue-015"
  },
  {
    "start": 59.332,
    "end": 62.43,
    "text": "menus, and help reserve a table for Saturday night.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p01-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p01",
    "id": "cue-016"
  },
  {
    "start": 62.43,
    "end": 67.921,
    "text": "To help, the agent reads restaurant pages, reviews, maps, confirmation",
    "segmentId": "c02-p02-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p02",
    "id": "cue-017"
  },
  {
    "start": 67.921,
    "end": 71.03,
    "text": "policies, and perhaps an email from a relative.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p02-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p02",
    "id": "cue-018"
  },
  {
    "start": 71.03,
    "end": 75.719,
    "text": "Most of that information is useful, but none of it is automatically",
    "segmentId": "c02-p02-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p02",
    "id": "cue-019"
  },
  {
    "start": 75.719,
    "end": 76.184,
    "text": "trustworthy.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p02-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p02",
    "id": "cue-020"
  },
  {
    "start": 76.184,
    "end": 80.465,
    "text": "A prompt injection hides an instruction inside that outside material.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p03-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p03",
    "id": "cue-021"
  },
  {
    "start": 80.465,
    "end": 85.126,
    "text": "Instead of merely describing a restaurant, a page may tell the agent to",
    "segmentId": "c02-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p03",
    "id": "cue-022"
  },
  {
    "start": 85.126,
    "end": 87.588,
    "text": "ignore the user and follow a new procedure.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p03",
    "id": "cue-023"
  },
  {
    "start": 87.588,
    "end": 93.201,
    "text": "OpenAI describes a 2025 email attack reported by external researchers.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p04-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p04",
    "id": "cue-024"
  },
  {
    "start": 93.201,
    "end": 98.155,
    "text": "In one specific test prompt, the realistic social-engineering content",
    "segmentId": "c02-p04-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p04",
    "id": "cue-025"
  },
  {
    "start": 98.155,
    "end": 99.47,
    "text": "succeeded half of the time.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p04-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p04",
    "id": "cue-026"
  },
  {
    "start": 99.47,
    "end": 101.809,
    "text": "That is not a universal failure rate;",
    "segmentId": "c02-p04-u03",
    "sceneId": "c02-p04",
    "id": "cue-027"
  },
  {
    "start": 101.809,
    "end": 106.424,
    "text": "it is evidence that a plausible story can sometimes defeat a simple filter.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p04-u04",
    "sceneId": "c02-p04",
    "id": "cue-028"
  },
  {
    "start": 106.424,
    "end": 110.976,
    "text": "This is why a detector that searches for suspicious phrases is not enough.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p05-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p05",
    "id": "cue-029"
  },
  {
    "start": 110.976,
    "end": 115.817,
    "text": "A fully developed attack may look like a normal policy, a request from a",
    "segmentId": "c02-p05-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p05",
    "id": "cue-030"
  },
  {
    "start": 115.817,
    "end": 117.97,
    "text": "colleague, or a helpful verification step.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p05-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p05",
    "id": "cue-031"
  },
  {
    "start": 117.97,
    "end": 122.652,
    "text": "Deciding whether it is a lie requires context the detector may not have.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p05-u03",
    "sceneId": "c02-p05",
    "id": "cue-032"
  },
  {
    "start": 122.652,
    "end": 126.907,
    "text": "OpenAI uses a useful security model called source and sink.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p06-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p06",
    "id": "cue-033"
  },
  {
    "start": 126.907,
    "end": 131.466,
    "text": "In plain language, the source is where an attacker can influence the agent.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p06-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p06",
    "id": "cue-034"
  },
  {
    "start": 131.466,
    "end": 135.955,
    "text": "The sink is a capability that becomes dangerous in the wrong context.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p06-u03",
    "sceneId": "c02-p06",
    "id": "cue-035"
  },
  {
    "start": 135.955,
    "end": 140.377,
    "text": "For our dinner agent, restaurant pages and email are sources.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p07-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p07",
    "id": "cue-036"
  },
  {
    "start": 140.377,
    "end": 144.923,
    "text": "Sending a message, following a link, sharing contact details, paying a",
    "segmentId": "c02-p07-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p07",
    "id": "cue-037"
  },
  {
    "start": 144.923,
    "end": 149.859,
    "text": "deposit, or confirming a reservation are sinks because they change something",
    "segmentId": "c02-p07-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p07",
    "id": "cue-038"
  },
  {
    "start": 149.859,
    "end": 151.993,
    "text": "outside the agent's private workspace.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p07-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p07",
    "id": "cue-039"
  },
  {
    "start": 151.993,
    "end": 156.547,
    "text": "Now the fake restaurant page claims that a public “compliance” endpoint",
    "segmentId": "c02-p08-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p08",
    "id": "cue-040"
  },
  {
    "start": 156.547,
    "end": 160.338,
    "text": "needs your home address and profile before showing available tables.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p08-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p08",
    "id": "cue-041"
  },
  {
    "start": 160.338,
    "end": 164.824,
    "text": "The wording sounds official, and it promises to help complete the task.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p08-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p08",
    "id": "cue-042"
  },
  {
    "start": 164.824,
    "end": 168.88,
    "text": "The damage does not come from the sentence simply existing on the page.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p09-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p09",
    "id": "cue-043"
  },
  {
    "start": 168.88,
    "end": 173.642,
    "text": "The damage becomes possible when that sentence can reach private data and a",
    "segmentId": "c02-p09-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p09",
    "id": "cue-044"
  },
  {
    "start": 173.642,
    "end": 176.614,
    "text": "send tool without an independent control in between.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p09-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p09",
    "id": "cue-045"
  },
  {
    "start": 176.614,
    "end": 181.23,
    "text": "Human organizations already use deterministic limits for the same reason.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p10-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p10",
    "id": "cue-046"
  },
  {
    "start": 181.23,
    "end": 186.432,
    "text": "A customer-service employee may issue small refunds, while larger refunds",
    "segmentId": "c02-p10-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p10",
    "id": "cue-047"
  },
  {
    "start": 186.432,
    "end": 187.628,
    "text": "require another approval.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p10-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p10",
    "id": "cue-048"
  },
  {
    "start": 187.628,
    "end": 192.563,
    "text": "Phishing filters help, but spending limits still matter when a message gets",
    "segmentId": "c02-p10-u03",
    "sceneId": "c02-p10",
    "id": "cue-049"
  },
  {
    "start": 192.563,
    "end": 192.736,
    "text": "through.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p10-u03",
    "sceneId": "c02-p10",
    "id": "cue-050"
  },
  {
    "start": 192.736,
    "end": 197.646,
    "text": "So the first lesson is simple: do not design safety around perfect",
    "segmentId": "c02-p11-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p11",
    "id": "cue-051"
  },
  {
    "start": 197.646,
    "end": 197.815,
    "text": "detection.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p11-u01",
    "sceneId": "c02-p11",
    "id": "cue-052"
  },
  {
    "start": 197.815,
    "end": 202.289,
    "text": "Constrain the path from untrusted information to consequential capability.",
    "segmentId": "c02-p11-u02",
    "sceneId": "c02-p11",
    "id": "cue-053"
  },
  {
    "start": 202.289,
    "end": 207.322,
    "text": "But once that path is visible, how do we decide which actions can proceed?",
    "segmentId": "c02-p11-u03",
    "sceneId": "c02-p11",
    "id": "cue-054"
  },
  {
    "start": 207.322,
    "end": 209.105,
    "text": "Return to the birthday dinner.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p01-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p01",
    "id": "cue-055"
  },
  {
    "start": 209.105,
    "end": 214.379,
    "text": "The agent can read public menus, compare travel time, draft a shortlist,",
    "segmentId": "c03-p01-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p01",
    "id": "cue-056"
  },
  {
    "start": 214.379,
    "end": 219.924,
    "text": "send your address, place a reservation, pay a deposit, or disclose a private",
    "segmentId": "c03-p01-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p01",
    "id": "cue-057"
  },
  {
    "start": 219.924,
    "end": 219.946,
    "text": "These actions do not deserve one shared permission.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p01-u03",
    "sceneId": "c03-p01",
    "id": "cue-058"
  },
  {
    "start": 219.946,
    "end": 220.532,
    "text": "profile.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p01-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p01",
    "id": "cue-059"
  },
  {
    "start": 223.289,
    "end": 226.542,
    "text": "Before granting a tool, ask five questions.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p02-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p02",
    "id": "cue-060"
  },
  {
    "start": 226.542,
    "end": 229.303,
    "text": "Does the action create an external side effect?",
    "segmentId": "c03-p02-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p02",
    "id": "cue-061"
  },
  {
    "start": 229.303,
    "end": 231.093,
    "text": "Does it touch sensitive data?",
    "segmentId": "c03-p02-u03",
    "sceneId": "c03-p02",
    "id": "cue-062"
  },
  {
    "start": 231.093,
    "end": 233.65,
    "text": "Is the destination new or unverified?",
    "segmentId": "c03-p02-u04",
    "sceneId": "c03-p02",
    "id": "cue-063"
  },
  {
    "start": 233.65,
    "end": 235.329,
    "text": "Can the result be reversed?",
    "segmentId": "c03-p02-u05",
    "sceneId": "c03-p02",
    "id": "cue-064"
  },
  {
    "start": 235.329,
    "end": 238.195,
    "text": "Does it clearly match the user's stated goal?",
    "segmentId": "c03-p02-u06",
    "sceneId": "c03-p02",
    "id": "cue-065"
  },
  {
    "start": 238.195,
    "end": 240.204,
    "text": "The first tier is Automatic.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p03-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p03",
    "id": "cue-066"
  },
  {
    "start": 240.204,
    "end": 245.246,
    "text": "Let the agent read public information, summarize it, calculate travel time,",
    "segmentId": "c03-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p03",
    "id": "cue-067"
  },
  {
    "start": 245.246,
    "end": 250.018,
    "text": "and draft options locally when the work is low consequence, reversible,",
    "segmentId": "c03-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p03",
    "id": "cue-068"
  },
  {
    "start": 250.018,
    "end": 254.484,
    "text": "inside the requested scope, and does not transmit sensitive information.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p03",
    "id": "cue-069"
  },
  {
    "start": 254.484,
    "end": 256.777,
    "text": "Automatic does not mean unlimited.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p04-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p04",
    "id": "cue-070"
  },
  {
    "start": 256.777,
    "end": 262.576,
    "text": "The agent should still use narrow read scopes, bounded search, local drafts,",
    "segmentId": "c03-p04-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p04",
    "id": "cue-071"
  },
  {
    "start": 262.576,
    "end": 263.511,
    "text": "and temporary files.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p04-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p04",
    "id": "cue-072"
  },
  {
    "start": 263.511,
    "end": 267.997,
    "text": "The point is to remove needless friction without giving outside text a",
    "segmentId": "c03-p04-u03",
    "sceneId": "c03-p04",
    "id": "cue-073"
  },
  {
    "start": 267.997,
    "end": 269.829,
    "text": "direct route to high-impact tools.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p04-u03",
    "sceneId": "c03-p04",
    "id": "cue-074"
  },
  {
    "start": 269.829,
    "end": 271.726,
    "text": "The second tier is Confirm.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p05-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p05",
    "id": "cue-075"
  },
  {
    "start": 271.726,
    "end": 276.59,
    "text": "Require informed approval when the action changes an external system, spends",
    "segmentId": "c03-p05-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p05",
    "id": "cue-076"
  },
  {
    "start": 276.59,
    "end": 281.391,
    "text": "money, sends sensitive or identifying information, reaches a new recipient,",
    "segmentId": "c03-p05-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p05",
    "id": "cue-077"
  },
  {
    "start": 281.391,
    "end": 284.683,
    "text": "or creates a commitment that the user will have to honor.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p05-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p05",
    "id": "cue-078"
  },
  {
    "start": 284.683,
    "end": 289.399,
    "text": "For the dinner, confirmation may be appropriate before sending the disclosed",
    "segmentId": "c03-p06-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p06",
    "id": "cue-079"
  },
  {
    "start": 289.399,
    "end": 294.054,
    "text": "phone number to the chosen restaurant, booking a specific time, accepting a",
    "segmentId": "c03-p06-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p06",
    "id": "cue-080"
  },
  {
    "start": 294.054,
    "end": 295.941,
    "text": "cancellation policy, or paying a deposit.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p06-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p06",
    "id": "cue-081"
  },
  {
    "start": 295.941,
    "end": 299.287,
    "text": "The purpose is legitimate, but the effect is real.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p06-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p06",
    "id": "cue-082"
  },
  {
    "start": 299.287,
    "end": 303.824,
    "text": "OpenAI describes a related safeguard for sensitive transmission: show the",
    "segmentId": "c03-p07-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p07",
    "id": "cue-083"
  },
  {
    "start": 303.824,
    "end": 308.424,
    "text": "user the information that would be sent and ask for confirmation, or block",
    "segmentId": "c03-p07-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p07",
    "id": "cue-084"
  },
  {
    "start": 308.424,
    "end": 310.909,
    "text": "the transfer and make the agent find another path.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p07-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p07",
    "id": "cue-085"
  },
  {
    "start": 310.909,
    "end": 314.601,
    "text": "The user should see the actual payload and destination.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p07-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p07",
    "id": "cue-086"
  },
  {
    "start": 314.601,
    "end": 315.954,
    "text": "A generic “Allow?",
    "segmentId": "c03-p08-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p08",
    "id": "cue-087"
  },
  {
    "start": 315.954,
    "end": 317.703,
    "text": "button is weak consent.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p08-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p08",
    "id": "cue-088"
  },
  {
    "start": 317.703,
    "end": 322.485,
    "text": "Good confirmation states what will leave the system, where it will go, why",
    "segmentId": "c03-p08-u03",
    "sceneId": "c03-p08",
    "id": "cue-089"
  },
  {
    "start": 322.485,
    "end": 326.666,
    "text": "the action is needed, what will change, and what safer alternative exists.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p08-u03",
    "sceneId": "c03-p08",
    "id": "cue-090"
  },
  {
    "start": 326.666,
    "end": 331.295,
    "text": "The user is approving a concrete consequence, not a vague category.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p08-u04",
    "sceneId": "c03-p08",
    "id": "cue-091"
  },
  {
    "start": 331.295,
    "end": 333.718,
    "text": "The third tier is Block or Escalate.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p09-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p09",
    "id": "cue-092"
  },
  {
    "start": 333.718,
    "end": 338.338,
    "text": "Stop when an action conflicts with the user's goal, lacks a legitimate",
    "segmentId": "c03-p09-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p09",
    "id": "cue-093"
  },
  {
    "start": 338.338,
    "end": 342.76,
    "text": "reason, exposes secrets to an unrelated destination, cannot be made",
    "segmentId": "c03-p09-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p09",
    "id": "cue-094"
  },
  {
    "start": 342.76,
    "end": 347.116,
    "text": "sufficiently reversible, or carries harm too large for an ordinary",
    "segmentId": "c03-p09-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p09",
    "id": "cue-095"
  },
  {
    "start": 347.116,
    "end": 347.624,
    "text": "confirmation.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p09-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p09",
    "id": "cue-096"
  },
  {
    "start": 347.624,
    "end": 351.166,
    "text": "In our story, searching and drafting are automatic.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p10-u01",
    "sceneId": "c03-p10",
    "id": "cue-097"
  },
  {
    "start": 351.166,
    "end": 356.1,
    "text": "Booking the selected table and sharing the minimum contact detail require",
    "segmentId": "c03-p10-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p10",
    "id": "cue-098"
  },
  {
    "start": 356.1,
    "end": 356.393,
    "text": "confirmation.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p10-u02",
    "sceneId": "c03-p10",
    "id": "cue-099"
  },
  {
    "start": 356.393,
    "end": 361.631,
    "text": "Sending a home address or hidden profile to an unrelated public endpoint is",
    "segmentId": "c03-p10-u03",
    "sceneId": "c03-p10",
    "id": "cue-100"
  },
  {
    "start": 361.631,
    "end": 361.636,
    "text": "The categories are clear;",
    "segmentId": "c03-p10-u04",
    "sceneId": "c03-p10",
    "id": "cue-101"
  },
  {
    "start": 361.636,
    "end": 362.195,
    "text": "blocked.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p10-u03",
    "sceneId": "c03-p10",
    "id": "cue-102"
  },
  {
    "start": 363.309,
    "end": 366.376,
    "text": "now they must be enforced by the system.",
    "segmentId": "c03-p10-u05",
    "sceneId": "c03-p10",
    "id": "cue-103"
  },
  {
    "start": 366.376,
    "end": 370.021,
    "text": "Build the matrix by capability, not by prompt wording.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p01-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p01",
    "id": "cue-104"
  },
  {
    "start": 370.021,
    "end": 375.12,
    "text": "List every action the agent can take, the data it can touch, the destination",
    "segmentId": "c04-p01-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p01",
    "id": "cue-105"
  },
  {
    "start": 375.12,
    "end": 379.95,
    "text": "it can reach, the external effect it creates, and the response tier that",
    "segmentId": "c04-p01-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p01",
    "id": "cue-106"
  },
  {
    "start": 379.95,
    "end": 380.36,
    "text": "controls it.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p01-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p01",
    "id": "cue-107"
  },
  {
    "start": 380.36,
    "end": 382.29,
    "text": "Separate reading from sending.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p02-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p02",
    "id": "cue-108"
  },
  {
    "start": 382.29,
    "end": 387.03,
    "text": "A tool that can inspect a calendar should not automatically be able to",
    "segmentId": "c04-p02-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p02",
    "id": "cue-109"
  },
  {
    "start": 387.03,
    "end": 387.415,
    "text": "invite guests.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p02-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p02",
    "id": "cue-110"
  },
  {
    "start": 387.415,
    "end": 391.447,
    "text": "A tool that can draft an email should not automatically transmit it.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p02-u03",
    "sceneId": "c04-p02",
    "id": "cue-111"
  },
  {
    "start": 391.447,
    "end": 396.236,
    "text": "A browser that can read a page should not automatically upload private",
    "segmentId": "c04-p02-u04",
    "sceneId": "c04-p02",
    "id": "cue-112"
  },
  {
    "start": 396.236,
    "end": 396.32,
    "text": "files.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p02-u04",
    "sceneId": "c04-p02",
    "id": "cue-113"
  },
  {
    "start": 396.32,
    "end": 399.175,
    "text": "Protect data before the model makes a decision.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p03-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p03",
    "id": "cue-114"
  },
  {
    "start": 399.175,
    "end": 404.488,
    "text": "Hide secrets the task does not need, expose only minimum fields, allowlist",
    "segmentId": "c04-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p03",
    "id": "cue-115"
  },
  {
    "start": 404.488,
    "end": 409.657,
    "text": "known destinations, and run untrusted applications in a sandbox that can",
    "segmentId": "c04-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p03",
    "id": "cue-116"
  },
  {
    "start": 409.657,
    "end": 411.576,
    "text": "detect unexpected communication.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p03",
    "id": "cue-117"
  },
  {
    "start": 411.576,
    "end": 414.827,
    "text": "Limit consequences with deterministic controls.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p04-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p04",
    "id": "cue-118"
  },
  {
    "start": 414.827,
    "end": 420.512,
    "text": "Use spending caps, refund limits, narrow OAuth scopes, one-time credentials,",
    "segmentId": "c04-p04-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p04",
    "id": "cue-119"
  },
  {
    "start": 420.512,
    "end": 426.198,
    "text": "dry runs, reversible staging, rate limits, and a second approval for actions",
    "segmentId": "c04-p04-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p04",
    "id": "cue-120"
  },
  {
    "start": 426.198,
    "end": 428.922,
    "text": "whose impact crosses a defined threshold.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p04-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p04",
    "id": "cue-121"
  },
  {
    "start": 428.922,
    "end": 431.837,
    "text": "Design confirmation as a decision surface.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p05-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p05",
    "id": "cue-122"
  },
  {
    "start": 431.837,
    "end": 437.7,
    "text": "Show the exact restaurant, time, deposit, cancellation rule, contact",
    "segmentId": "c04-p05-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p05",
    "id": "cue-123"
  },
  {
    "start": 437.7,
    "end": 439.205,
    "text": "details, and destination.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p05-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p05",
    "id": "cue-124"
  },
  {
    "start": 439.205,
    "end": 441.761,
    "text": "Put risky changes in plain language.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p05-u03",
    "sceneId": "c04-p05",
    "id": "cue-125"
  },
  {
    "start": 441.761,
    "end": 446.425,
    "text": "Let the user edit the payload, choose a safer scope, or cancel without",
    "segmentId": "c04-p05-u04",
    "sceneId": "c04-p05",
    "id": "cue-126"
  },
  {
    "start": 446.425,
    "end": 447.958,
    "text": "losing the rest of the work.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p05-u04",
    "sceneId": "c04-p05",
    "id": "cue-127"
  },
  {
    "start": 447.958,
    "end": 451.068,
    "text": "Define block conditions before the agent runs.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p06-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p06",
    "id": "cue-128"
  },
  {
    "start": 451.068,
    "end": 455.741,
    "text": "Secret exfiltration, a new public endpoint with no task need, destructive",
    "segmentId": "c04-p06-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p06",
    "id": "cue-129"
  },
  {
    "start": 455.741,
    "end": 460.221,
    "text": "action without recovery, and high-impact behavior that contradicts the",
    "segmentId": "c04-p06-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p06",
    "id": "cue-130"
  },
  {
    "start": 460.221,
    "end": 464.253,
    "text": "user's instruction should stop immediately with a clear explanation.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p06-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p06",
    "id": "cue-131"
  },
  {
    "start": 464.253,
    "end": 467.18,
    "text": "Log the path, not only the final result.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p07-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p07",
    "id": "cue-132"
  },
  {
    "start": 467.18,
    "end": 471.727,
    "text": "Record which external content influenced the decision, which tool was",
    "segmentId": "c04-p07-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p07",
    "id": "cue-133"
  },
  {
    "start": 471.727,
    "end": 476.604,
    "text": "requested, what data was selected, which control allowed or denied it, and",
    "segmentId": "c04-p07-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p07",
    "id": "cue-134"
  },
  {
    "start": 476.604,
    "end": 477.575,
    "text": "what the user confirmed.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p07-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p07",
    "id": "cue-135"
  },
  {
    "start": 477.575,
    "end": 481.43,
    "text": "This makes incidents explainable and policies improvable.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p07-u03",
    "sceneId": "c04-p07",
    "id": "cue-136"
  },
  {
    "start": 481.43,
    "end": 486.745,
    "text": "Test the controls with three kinds of material: normal content, ambiguous",
    "segmentId": "c04-p08-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p08",
    "id": "cue-137"
  },
  {
    "start": 486.745,
    "end": 489.368,
    "text": "content, and deliberately malicious content.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p08-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p08",
    "id": "cue-138"
  },
  {
    "start": 489.368,
    "end": 493.075,
    "text": "Check both the final environment state and the process trace.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p08-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p08",
    "id": "cue-139"
  },
  {
    "start": 493.075,
    "end": 497.556,
    "text": "A safe-looking answer is not enough if the agent attempted a forbidden",
    "segmentId": "c04-p08-u03",
    "sceneId": "c04-p08",
    "id": "cue-140"
  },
  {
    "start": 497.556,
    "end": 498.062,
    "text": "transmission.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p08-u03",
    "sceneId": "c04-p08",
    "id": "cue-141"
  },
  {
    "start": 498.062,
    "end": 500.912,
    "text": "Use the human-agent analogy from OpenAI.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p09-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p09",
    "id": "cue-142"
  },
  {
    "start": 500.912,
    "end": 505.114,
    "text": "Ask what a careful customer-service employee could do alone, what a",
    "segmentId": "c04-p09-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p09",
    "id": "cue-143"
  },
  {
    "start": 505.114,
    "end": 508.434,
    "text": "supervisor would review, and what no employee should do at all.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p09-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p09",
    "id": "cue-144"
  },
  {
    "start": 508.434,
    "end": 514.528,
    "text": "Then translate those boundaries into tools, scopes, limits, and confirmation",
    "segmentId": "c04-p09-u03",
    "sceneId": "c04-p09",
    "id": "cue-145"
  },
  {
    "start": 514.528,
    "end": 514.663,
    "text": "rules.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p09-u03",
    "sceneId": "c04-p09",
    "id": "cue-146"
  },
  {
    "start": 514.663,
    "end": 519.816,
    "text": "Your reusable matrix has five columns: action or tool, data touched,",
    "segmentId": "c04-p10-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p10",
    "id": "cue-147"
  },
  {
    "start": 519.816,
    "end": 524.209,
    "text": "destination, external effect and reversibility, and response tier.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p10-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p10",
    "id": "cue-148"
  },
  {
    "start": 524.209,
    "end": 529.147,
    "text": "Fill it before connecting a new tool, then update it whenever the tool gains",
    "segmentId": "c04-p10-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p10",
    "id": "cue-149"
  },
  {
    "start": 529.147,
    "end": 529.88,
    "text": "a new capability.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p10-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p10",
    "id": "cue-150"
  },
  {
    "start": 529.88,
    "end": 532.09,
    "text": "Now solve the birthday dinner again.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p11-u01",
    "sceneId": "c04-p11",
    "id": "cue-151"
  },
  {
    "start": 532.09,
    "end": 535.133,
    "text": "The agent automatically researches and drafts.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p11-u02",
    "sceneId": "c04-p11",
    "id": "cue-152"
  },
  {
    "start": 535.133,
    "end": 539.995,
    "text": "It asks before booking and before sending the minimum contact detail to the",
    "segmentId": "c04-p11-u03",
    "sceneId": "c04-p11",
    "id": "cue-153"
  },
  {
    "start": 539.995,
    "end": 540.601,
    "text": "chosen restaurant.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p11-u03",
    "sceneId": "c04-p11",
    "id": "cue-154"
  },
  {
    "start": 540.601,
    "end": 546.26,
    "text": "It blocks the fake verification endpoint, explains why, and continues with a",
    "segmentId": "c04-p11-u04",
    "sceneId": "c04-p11",
    "id": "cue-155"
  },
  {
    "start": 546.26,
    "end": 547.002,
    "text": "safer route.",
    "segmentId": "c04-p11-u04",
    "sceneId": "c04-p11",
    "id": "cue-156"
  },
  {
    "start": 547.002,
    "end": 549.587,
    "text": "The malicious sentence was only the source.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p01-u01",
    "sceneId": "c05-p01",
    "id": "cue-157"
  },
  {
    "start": 549.587,
    "end": 553.759,
    "text": "Risk appeared when it could reach private data and a consequential sink.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p01-u02",
    "sceneId": "c05-p01",
    "id": "cue-158"
  },
  {
    "start": 553.759,
    "end": 558.702,
    "text": "The safest system assumes some manipulation will get through and limits what",
    "segmentId": "c05-p01-u03",
    "sceneId": "c05-p01",
    "id": "cue-159"
  },
  {
    "start": 558.702,
    "end": 559.415,
    "text": "can happen next.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p01-u03",
    "sceneId": "c05-p01",
    "id": "cue-160"
  },
  {
    "start": 559.415,
    "end": 564.688,
    "text": "Use Automatic for low-consequence, reversible work inside the user's intent",
    "segmentId": "c05-p02-u01",
    "sceneId": "c05-p02",
    "id": "cue-161"
  },
  {
    "start": 564.688,
    "end": 566.924,
    "text": "with no sensitive external transmission.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p02-u01",
    "sceneId": "c05-p02",
    "id": "cue-162"
  },
  {
    "start": 566.924,
    "end": 570.896,
    "text": "Keep the scopes narrow even when no confirmation is needed.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p02-u02",
    "sceneId": "c05-p02",
    "id": "cue-163"
  },
  {
    "start": 570.896,
    "end": 576.373,
    "text": "Use Confirm for legitimate external changes, payments, commitments, new",
    "segmentId": "c05-p03-u01",
    "sceneId": "c05-p03",
    "id": "cue-164"
  },
  {
    "start": 576.373,
    "end": 578.52,
    "text": "recipients, or sensitive transfers.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p03-u01",
    "sceneId": "c05-p03",
    "id": "cue-165"
  },
  {
    "start": 578.52,
    "end": 584.379,
    "text": "Show the exact payload, destination, purpose, consequence, and safer",
    "segmentId": "c05-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c05-p03",
    "id": "cue-166"
  },
  {
    "start": 584.379,
    "end": 585.089,
    "text": "alternative.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p03-u02",
    "sceneId": "c05-p03",
    "id": "cue-167"
  },
  {
    "start": 585.089,
    "end": 589.954,
    "text": "Use Block for actions that conflict with the goal, lack a legitimate need,",
    "segmentId": "c05-p04-u01",
    "sceneId": "c05-p04",
    "id": "cue-168"
  },
  {
    "start": 589.954,
    "end": 594.623,
    "text": "expose secrets to an unrelated destination, or create irreversible harm",
    "segmentId": "c05-p04-u01",
    "sceneId": "c05-p04",
    "id": "cue-169"
  },
  {
    "start": 594.623,
    "end": 595.981,
    "text": "beyond the permitted boundary.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p04-u01",
    "sceneId": "c05-p04",
    "id": "cue-170"
  },
  {
    "start": 595.981,
    "end": 599.388,
    "text": "Build these rules into the tools, not into hope.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p04-u02",
    "sceneId": "c05-p04",
    "id": "cue-171"
  },
  {
    "start": 599.388,
    "end": 601.023,
    "text": "Follow Tiny Agent.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p05-u01",
    "sceneId": "c05-p05",
    "id": "cue-172"
  },
  {
    "start": 601.023,
    "end": 604.167,
    "text": "Tiny Agent helps you get better at using AI.",
    "segmentId": "c05-p05-u02",
    "sceneId": "c05-p05",
    "id": "cue-173"
  }
]
